优惠，包括手机、智能手表、耳机、充电器、玩具和各种配件。并非所有的优惠都是黑色星期五的剩菜。其他小工具现在甚至更便宜，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation/dp/B07K1WWBJK?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener &quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;第二代 Apple Pencil&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09M8LG59J?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;provided nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Yeedi Vac 2 Pro&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F% 2Fnanoleaf.me%2Fen-US%2Fproducts%2Fnanoleaf-shapes%2F%3Fcategory%3Dultra-black-triangles%26pack%3Dsmarter-kit%26size%3D9&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww。 theverge.com%2F23973013%2Fcyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Nanoleaf 形状超黑...&lt;/a>;&lt;/ p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T11:43:26-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T11:43:26-05:00</updated><title>数字车钥匙就在这里。我们准备好了吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;数字车钥匙开门&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OR_5qmpeVunpUvRPbbgRKaBxkiA=/0x1:3000x2001/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/72906067/P90354782_highRes_bmw_digital_key_06_2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：宝马&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7T6nfn&quot;>;首先我们有手摇曲柄。然后是真正的钥匙，然后是钥匙扣。现在我们有了“数字钥匙”，您可以通过手机锁定、解锁和启动汽车。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eNuMvb&quot;>;数字钥匙仍然很少见，仅在少数型号中提供。在数字密钥技术普及之前，还有很多问题需要解决。应使用哪种技术：近场通信 (NFC)？超宽带（UWB）？蓝牙？我们如何确保它免受黑客攻击？当你的手机电池没电时会发生什么？ （剧透：它仍然可以工作。）&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;xEdD9s&quot;>;许多汽车制造商已经提供数字钥匙，但它并不总是能完美地工作。特斯拉表示只会为 Model 3 提供数字钥匙，但后来选择了......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23970875/digital-car- key-iphone-unlock-start-ccc-standard&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23970875/digital-car-key-iphone-unlock-start-ccc-standard" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23970875/digital-car-key-iphone-unlock-start-ccc-standard</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T11:38:24-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T11:38:24-05:00</updated><title> Roomba 最新机器人吸尘器网络星期一最高立减 400 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XBt4mBTqJEESqqR2L4H43sqNQ1I=/0x0:5760x3840/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72903445 /8A0A0511.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;iRobot 的旗舰扫地机器人 j9 Combo Plus 网络星期一优惠 400 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;4Rgsy2&quot;>;与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973681/amazons -irobot-acquisition-likely-to-get-big-thumbs-up-from-eu&quot;>;新主人即将到来&lt;/a>;，iRobot 已经通过今年降低其全新吸尘器的价格进入亚马逊折扣游戏网络星期一。周五，它推出了新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/28/23845899/irobot-roomba-combo-j5-plus-robot-vacuum-mop-price&quot;>;预算和中档产品线&lt;/a>;、Roomba Combo i5 Plus 和 Combo j5 Plus，周日，iRobot 将其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/11/23864923 降价 400 美元/irobot-roomba-combo-j9-plus-robot-vacuum-mop-price-features&quot;>;全新顶级型号&lt;/a>;：j9 Plus 和 Combo j9 Plus。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;2mIqaI&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊购买了 iRobot 来查看您的房屋内部&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23293687/amazon-irobot-acquisition-purchase-smarthome-intelligence-隐私分析&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Roomba j7 Plus 评论：现在顶部有拖把&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23489768/irobot-roomba-combo-j7- plus-robot-vacuum-mop-review&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;6mIW22&quot;>;Roomba j9 Plus 是该公司的新款旗舰扫地机器人，现已发售&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Roomba-Self-Emptying-Robot-Vacuum/dp/B0C415NHBM/?tag=theverge02- 售价 599 美元，&lt;strong>; &lt;/strong>;低于 899 美元20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ck5siAuIR75&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot; https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wellbots.com%2Fproducts%2Firobot-roomba-j9-robot-vacuum&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp; sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F26%2F23976565%2Firobot-roomba-j9-j5-i5-robot-vacuum-cyber-monday-deal“rel =“赞助nofollow noopener”目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Wellbots&lt;/a>;。它配备了一个自空底座和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22997597/best-robot-vacuum-cleaner#:~:text=iRobot%20Roomba%20j7&amp;amp; 的所有智能功能。 text=With%20the%20best%20AI%2Dpowered,at%20getting%20your%20floor%20clean.&quot;>;Roomba j7&lt;/a>;，包括人工智能驱动的避障功能，可避开电线、衣服、鞋子等家庭杂物和宠物粪便，加上比以前更高的吸力......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/26/23976565/irobot-roomba-j9 -j5-i5-robot-vacuum-cyber-monday-deal&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/26/23976565/irobot-roomba-j9-j5-i5-robot-vacuum-cyber-monday-deal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/26/23976565/irobot-roomba-j9-j5-i5-robot-vacuum-cyber-monday-deal</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T11:36:40-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T11:36:40-05:00</updated><title>智能手表和健身追踪器的网络星期一最佳优惠</title><cont